{
  "video_id": "lhoCdZFoktQ",
  "title": "The journey through loss and grief | Jason B. Rosenthal",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13870.0,
      "end_time": 16400.0,
      "text": "There are three words that explain why I am here."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17400.0,
      "end_time": 21959.0,
      "text": "They are \"Amy Krouse Rosenthal.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23320.0,
      "end_time": 24816.0,
      "text": "At the end of Amy's life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24840.0,
      "end_time": 27360.0,
      "text": "hyped up on morphine and home in hospice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28239.0,
      "end_time": 30816.0,
      "text": "the \"New York Times\" published an article she wrote"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30840.0,
      "end_time": 33920.0,
      "text": "for the \"Modern Love\" column on March 3, 2017."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35160.0,
      "end_time": 37879.0,
      "text": "It was read worldwide by over five million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39160.0,
      "end_time": 42656.0,
      "text": "The piece was unbearably sad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42680.0,
      "end_time": 44415.0,
      "text": "ironically funny"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44439.0,
      "end_time": 46000.0,
      "text": "and brutally honest."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47200.0,
      "end_time": 49856.0,
      "text": "While it was certainly about our life together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49880.0,
      "end_time": 52280.0,
      "text": "the focus of the piece was me."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53440.0,
      "end_time": 56576.0,
      "text": "It was called, \"You May Want to Marry My Husband.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56600.0,
      "end_time": 59640.0,
      "text": "It was a creative play on a personal ad for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60440.0,
      "end_time": 64176.0,
      "text": "Amy quite literally left an empty space for me to fill"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 64200.0,
      "end_time": 66000.0,
      "text": "with another love story."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67520.0,
      "end_time": 69479.0,
      "text": "Amy was my wife for half my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70360.0,
      "end_time": 75960.0,
      "text": "She was my partner in raising three wonderful, now grown children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 75120.0,
      "end_time": 77135.0,
      "text": "and really, she was my girl, you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77160.0,
      "end_time": 79800.0,
      "text": "We had so much in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 80360.0,
      "end_time": 81896.0,
      "text": "We loved the same art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81920.0,
      "end_time": 84536.0,
      "text": "the same documentaries, the same music."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84560.0,
      "end_time": 87416.0,
      "text": "Music was a huge part of our life together."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87440.0,
      "end_time": 89280.0,
      "text": "And we shared the same values."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90160.0,
      "end_time": 91576.0,
      "text": "We were in love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91600.0,
      "end_time": 95520.0,
      "text": "and our love grew stronger up until her last day."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 97200.0,
      "end_time": 99560.0,
      "text": "Amy was a prolific author."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99800.0,
      "end_time": 101616.0,
      "text": "In addition to two groundbreaking memoirs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101640.0,
      "end_time": 104400.0,
      "text": "she published over 30 children's books."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105800.0,
      "end_time": 107856.0,
      "text": "Posthumously, the book she wrote with our daughter Paris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107880.0,
      "end_time": 109496.0,
      "text": "called \"Dear Girl,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109520.0,
      "end_time": 113000.0,
      "text": "reached the number one position on the \"New York Times\" bestseller list."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 114240.0,
      "end_time": 117160.0,
      "text": "She was a self-described tiny filmmaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117640.0,
      "end_time": 120776.0,
      "text": "She was 5'1\" and her films were not that long."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120800.0,
      "end_time": 121816.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121840.0,
      "end_time": 126240.0,
      "text": "Her films exemplified her natural ability to gather people together."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 127240.0,
      "end_time": 129656.0,
      "text": "She was also a terrific public speaker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 129680.0,
      "end_time": 132816.0,
      "text": "talking with children and adults of all ages"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132840.0,
      "end_time": 134400.0,
      "text": "all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135520.0,
      "end_time": 139816.0,
      "text": "Now, my story of grief is only unique in the sense of it being rather public."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139840.0,
      "end_time": 144640.0,
      "text": "However, the grieving process itself was not my story alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 145920.0,
      "end_time": 149399.0,
      "text": "Amy gave me permission to move forward, and I'm so grateful for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150400.0,
      "end_time": 153550.0,
      "text": "Now, just a little over a year into my new life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 153800.0,
      "end_time": 154520.0,
      "text": "I've learned a few things."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 155640.0,
      "end_time": 158655.0,
      "text": "I'm here to share with you part of the process of moving forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 158680.0,
      "end_time": 160720.0,
      "text": "through and with grief."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 162240.0,
      "end_time": 164656.0,
      "text": "But before I do that, I think it would be important"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 164680.0,
      "end_time": 166736.0,
      "text": "to talk a little bit about the end of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 166760.0,
      "end_time": 169560.0,
      "text": "because it forms how I have been emotionally since then."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 170800.0,
      "end_time": 173360.0,
      "text": "Death is such a taboo subject, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 174440.0,
      "end_time": 177920.0,
      "text": "Amy ate her last meal on January 9, 2017."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 178920.0,
      "end_time": 180976.0,
      "text": "She somehow lived an additional two months"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 181000.0,
      "end_time": 182240.0,
      "text": "without solid food."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 183480.0,
      "end_time": 187616.0,
      "text": "Her doctors told us we could do hospice at home"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 187640.0,
      "end_time": 188880.0,
      "text": "or in the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 189960.0,
      "end_time": 193936.0,
      "text": "They did not tell us that Amy would shrink to half her body weight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 193960.0,
      "end_time": 196696.0,
      "text": "that she would never lay with her husband again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 196720.0,
      "end_time": 200960.0,
      "text": "and that walking upstairs to our bedroom would soon feel like running a marathon."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 202880.0,
      "end_time": 207736.0,
      "text": "Home hospice does have an aura of being a beautiful environment to die in."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 207760.0,
      "end_time": 210576.0,
      "text": "How great that you don't have the sounds of machines beeping"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 210600.0,
      "end_time": 213216.0,
      "text": "and going on and off all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 213240.0,
      "end_time": 217136.0,
      "text": "no disruptions for mandatory drug administration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 217160.0,
      "end_time": 220840.0,
      "text": "home with your family to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 222640.0,
      "end_time": 226696.0,
      "text": "We did our best to make those weeks as meaningful as we could."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 226720.0,
      "end_time": 228736.0,
      "text": "We talked often about death."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 228760.0,
      "end_time": 232296.0,
      "text": "Everybody knows it's going to happen to them, like, for sure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 232320.0,
      "end_time": 235640.0,
      "text": "but being able to talk openly about it was liberating."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 237400.0,
      "end_time": 239280.0,
      "text": "We talked about subjects like parenting."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 240800.0,
      "end_time": 244840.0,
      "text": "I asked Amy how I could be the best parent possible to our children in her absence."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 246000.0,
      "end_time": 248576.0,
      "text": "In those conversations, she gave me confidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 248600.0,
      "end_time": 252136.0,
      "text": "by stressing what a great relationship I had with each one of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 252160.0,
      "end_time": 253840.0,
      "text": "and that I can do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 255400.0,
      "end_time": 257136.0,
      "text": "I know there will be many times"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 257160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260136.00000000003,
      "text": "where I wish she and I can make decisions together."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 260160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262360.0,
      "text": "We were always so in sync."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 264320.0,
      "end_time": 266816.0,
      "text": "May I be so audacious as to suggest"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 266840.0,
      "end_time": 270616.0,
      "text": "that you have these conversations now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 270640.0,
      "end_time": 272255.0,
      "text": "when healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 272279.0,
      "end_time": 274280.0,
      "text": "Please don't wait."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 276240.0,
      "end_time": 280256.0,
      "text": "As part of our hospice experience, we organized groups of visitors."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 280280.0,
      "end_time": 284400.0,
      "text": "How brave of Amy to receive them, even as she began her physical decline."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 285480.0,
      "end_time": 287160.0,
      "text": "We had a Krouse night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 287400.0,
      "end_time": 289416.0,
      "text": "her parents and three siblings."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 289440.0,
      "end_time": 291776.0,
      "text": "Friends and family were next."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 291800.0,
      "end_time": 294560.0,
      "text": "Each told beautiful stories of Amy and of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 295560.0,
      "end_time": 298480.0,
      "text": "Amy made an immense impact on her loyal friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 300960.0,
      "end_time": 304880.0,
      "text": "But home hospice is not so beautiful for the surviving family members."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 305800.0,
      "end_time": 309496.0,
      "text": "I want to get a little personal here and tell you that to this date,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 309520.0,
      "end_time": 312719.0,
      "text": "I have memories of those final weeks that haunt me."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 314560.0,
      "end_time": 317840.0,
      "text": "I remember walking backwards to the bathroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 318760.0,
      "end_time": 321390.0,
      "text": "assisting Amy with each step."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 321760.0,
      "end_time": 323240.0,
      "text": "I felt so strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 323920.0,
      "end_time": 325176.0,
      "text": "I'm not such a big guy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 325200.0,
      "end_time": 330479.0,
      "text": "but my arms looked and felt so healthy compared to Amy's frail body."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 331720.0,
      "end_time": 333960.0,
      "text": "And that body failed in our house."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 336640.0,
      "end_time": 338640.0,
      "text": "On March 13 of last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 340160.0,
      "end_time": 343880.0,
      "text": "my wife died of ovarian cancer in our bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 346920.0,
      "end_time": 348640.0,
      "text": "I carried her lifeless body"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 350360.0,
      "end_time": 351560.0,
      "text": "down our stairs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 353520.0,
      "end_time": 354719.0,
      "text": "through our dining room"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 356800.0,
      "end_time": 357280.0,
      "text": "and our living room"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 358600.0,
      "end_time": 359840.0,
      "text": "to a waiting gurney"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 361800.0,
      "end_time": 362640.0,
      "text": "to have her body cremated."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 364160.0,
      "end_time": 366240.0,
      "text": "I will never get that image out of my head."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 367240.0,
      "end_time": 370336.0,
      "text": "If you know someone who has been through the hospice experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 370360.0,
      "end_time": 371616.0,
      "text": "acknowledge that."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 371640.0,
      "end_time": 373256.0,
      "text": "Just say you heard this guy Jason"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 373280.0,
      "end_time": 375895.0,
      "text": "talk about how tough it must be to have those memories"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 375920.0,
      "end_time": 378736.0,
      "text": "and that you're there if they ever want to talk about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 378760.0,
      "end_time": 380776.0,
      "text": "They may not want to talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 380800.0,
      "end_time": 385840.0,
      "text": "but it's nice to connect with someone living each day with those lasting images."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 387280.0,
      "end_time": 390760.0,
      "text": "I know this sounds unbelievable, but I've never been asked that question."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 392600.0,
      "end_time": 395800.0,
      "text": "Amy's essay caused me to experience grief in a public way."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 397000.0,
      "end_time": 400680.0,
      "text": "Many of the readers who reached out to me wrote beautiful words of reflection."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 401520.0,
      "end_time": 404895.0,
      "text": "The scope of Amy's impact was deeper and richer"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 404920.0,
      "end_time": 407000.0,
      "text": "than even us and her family knew."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 408400.0,
      "end_time": 412215.0,
      "text": "Some of the responses I received helped me with the intense grieving process"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 412240.0,
      "end_time": 413440.0,
      "text": "because of their humor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 414440.0,
      "end_time": 416616.0,
      "text": "like this email I received from a woman reader"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 416640.0,
      "end_time": 419120.0,
      "text": "who read the article, declaring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 420160.0,
      "end_time": 422560.0,
      "text": "\"I will marry you when you are ready --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 422800.0,
      "end_time": 423656.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 423680.0,
      "end_time": 425760.0,
      "text": "\"provided you permanently stop drinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 427400.0,
      "end_time": 428480.0,
      "text": "No other conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 429560.0,
      "end_time": 431000.0,
      "text": "I promise to outlive you."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 431840.0,
      "end_time": 433280.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 434680.0,
      "end_time": 439160.0,
      "text": "Now, I do like a good tequila, but that really is not my issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 439400.0,
      "end_time": 441176.0,
      "text": "Yet how could I say no to that proposal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 441200.0,
      "end_time": 443256.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 443280.0,
      "end_time": 447200.0,
      "text": "I laughed through the tears when I read this note from a family friend:"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 448200.0,
      "end_time": 450896.0,
      "text": "\"I remember Shabbat dinners at your home"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 450920.0,
      "end_time": 454120.0,
      "text": "and Amy teaching me how to make cornbread croutons."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 454880.0,
      "end_time": 458560.0,
      "text": "Only Amy could find creativity in croutons.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 458580.0,
      "end_time": 459580.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 462520.0,
      "end_time": 466216.0,
      "text": "On July 27, just a few months after Amy's death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 466240.0,
      "end_time": 467856.0,
      "text": "my dad died of complications"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 467880.0,
      "end_time": 471320.0,
      "text": "related to a decades-long battle with Parkinson's disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 472400.0,
      "end_time": 475960.0,
      "text": "I had to wonder: How much can the human condition handle?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 476680.0,
      "end_time": 479896.0,
      "text": "What makes us capable of dealing with this intense loss"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 479920.0,
      "end_time": 481600.0,
      "text": "and yet carry on?"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 482360.0,
      "end_time": 484960.0,
      "text": "Was this a test?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 484120.0,
      "end_time": 486760.0,
      "text": "Why my family and my amazing children?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 488320.0,
      "end_time": 491640.0,
      "text": "Looking for answers, I regret to say, is a lifelong mission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 492440.0,
      "end_time": 496416.0,
      "text": "but the key to my being able to persevere"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 496440.0,
      "end_time": 500160.0,
      "text": "is Amy's expressed and very public edict"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 500400.0,
      "end_time": 501840.0,
      "text": "that I must go on."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 503520.0,
      "end_time": 505919.0,
      "text": "Throughout this year, I have done just that."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 506600.0,
      "end_time": 510776.0,
      "text": "I have attempted to step out and seek the joy and the beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 510800.0,
      "end_time": 514200.0,
      "text": "that I know this life is capable of providing."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 516320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517560.00000000006,
      "text": "But here's the reality:"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 518760.0,
      "end_time": 520560.0,
      "text": "those family gatherings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 520799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 522535.99999999994,
      "text": "attending weddings and events honoring Amy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 522558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 524575.0,
      "text": "as loving as they are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 524600.0,
      "end_time": 527200.0,
      "text": "have all been very difficult to endure."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 528240.0,
      "end_time": 529496.0,
      "text": "People say I'm amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 529520.0,
      "end_time": 532216.0,
      "text": "\"How do you handle yourself that way during those times?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 532240.0,
      "end_time": 534760.0,
      "text": "They say, \"You do it with such grace.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 536560.0,
      "end_time": 537760.0,
      "text": "Well, guess what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 538320.0,
      "end_time": 541200.0,
      "text": "I really am sad a lot of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 542160.0,
      "end_time": 545216.0,
      "text": "I often feel like I'm kind of a mess,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 545240.0,
      "end_time": 549376.0,
      "text": "and I know these feelings apply to other surviving spouses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 549400.0,
      "end_time": 551840.0,
      "text": "children, parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 552720.0,
      "end_time": 554200.0,
      "text": "and other family members."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 556000.0,
      "end_time": 558696.0,
      "text": "In Japanese Zen, there is a term \"Shoji,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 558720.0,
      "end_time": 561320.0,
      "text": "which translates as \"birth death.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 561920.0,
      "end_time": 564695.0,
      "text": "There is no separation between life and death"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 564720.0,
      "end_time": 567200.0,
      "text": "other than a thin line that connects the two."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 568280.0,
      "end_time": 572856.0,
      "text": "Birth, or the joyous, wonderful, vital parts of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 572880.0,
      "end_time": 575296.0,
      "text": "and death, those things we want to get rid of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 575320.0,
      "end_time": 577280.0,
      "text": "are said to be faced equally."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 578680.0,
      "end_time": 580856.0,
      "text": "In this new life that I find myself in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 580880.0,
      "end_time": 586000.0,
      "text": "I am doing my best to embrace this concept as I move forward with grieving."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 587480.0,
      "end_time": 589976.0,
      "text": "In the early months following Amy's death, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 590000.0,
      "end_time": 593696.0,
      "text": "I was sure that the feeling of despair would be ever-present,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 593720.0,
      "end_time": 595480.0,
      "text": "that it would be all-consuming."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 596960.0,
      "end_time": 600240.0,
      "text": "Soon I was fortunate to receive some promising advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 601680.0,
      "end_time": 603856.0,
      "text": "Many members of the losing-a-spouse club"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 603880.0,
      "end_time": 605800.0,
      "text": "reached out to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 605680.0,
      "end_time": 610335.0,
      "text": "One friend in particular who had also lost her life partner kept repeating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 610360.0,
      "end_time": 613560.0,
      "text": "\"Jason, you will find joy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 614560.0,
      "end_time": 616776.0,
      "text": "I didn't even know what she was talking about."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 616800.0,
      "end_time": 618359.0,
      "text": "How was that possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 619760.0,
      "end_time": 622456.0,
      "text": "But because Amy gave me very public permission"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 622480.0,
      "end_time": 624560.0,
      "text": "to also find happiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 625360.0,
      "end_time": 628400.0,
      "text": "I now have experienced joy from time to time."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 629880.0,
      "end_time": 634280.0,
      "text": "There it was, dancing the night away at an LCD Soundsystem concert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 635400.0,
      "end_time": 639336.0,
      "text": "traveling with my brother and best friend or with a college buddy on a boys' trip"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 639360.0,
      "end_time": 641680.0,
      "text": "to meet a group of great guys I never met before."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 642840.0,
      "end_time": 647696.0,
      "text": "From observing that my deck had sun beating down on it on a cold day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 647720.0,
      "end_time": 649976.0,
      "text": "stepping out in it, laying there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 650000.0,
      "end_time": 652280.0,
      "text": "the warmth consuming my body."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 654680.0,
      "end_time": 659000.0,
      "text": "The joy comes from my three stunning children."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 660920.0,
      "end_time": 662536.0,
      "text": "There was my son Justin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 662560.0,
      "end_time": 665175.0,
      "text": "texting me a picture of himself with an older gentleman"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 665200.0,
      "end_time": 670136.0,
      "text": "with a massive, strong forearm and the caption, \"I just met Popeye,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 670160.0,
      "end_time": 671856.0,
      "text": "with a huge grin on his face."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 671880.0,
      "end_time": 673336.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 673360.0,
      "end_time": 675896.0,
      "text": "There was his brother Miles, walking to the train"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 675920.0,
      "end_time": 678439.0,
      "text": "for his first day of work after graduating college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 679400.0,
      "end_time": 681496.0,
      "text": "who stopped and looked back at me and asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 681520.0,
      "end_time": 682760.0,
      "text": "\"What am I forgetting?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 683320.0,
      "end_time": 686880.0,
      "text": "I assured him right away, \"You are 100 percent ready. You got this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 688400.0,
      "end_time": 689856.0,
      "text": "And my daughter Paris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 689880.0,
      "end_time": 692896.0,
      "text": "walking together through Battersea Park in London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 692920.0,
      "end_time": 694736.0,
      "text": "the leaves piled high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 694760.0,
      "end_time": 698880.0,
      "text": "the sun glistening in the early morning on our way to yoga."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 700880.0,
      "end_time": 704136.0,
      "text": "I would add that beauty is also there to discover,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 704160.0,
      "end_time": 706576.0,
      "text": "and I mean beauty of the wabi-sabi variety"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 706600.0,
      "end_time": 708200.0,
      "text": "but beauty nonetheless."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 709160.0,
      "end_time": 712496.0,
      "text": "On the one hand, when I see something in this category, I want to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 712520.0,
      "end_time": 714936.0,
      "text": "\"Amy, did you see that? Did you hear that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 714960.0,
      "end_time": 717800.0,
      "text": "It's too beautiful for you not to share with me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 720320.0,
      "end_time": 721520.0,
      "text": "On the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 722800.0,
      "end_time": 724896.0,
      "text": "I now experience these moments"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 724920.0,
      "end_time": 726560.0,
      "text": "in an entirely new way."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 728600.0,
      "end_time": 731336.0,
      "text": "There was the beauty I found in music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 731360.0,
      "end_time": 734896.0,
      "text": "like the moment in the newest Manchester Orchestra album,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 734920.0,
      "end_time": 736216.0,
      "text": "when the song \"The Alien\""
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 736240.0,
      "end_time": 738760.0,
      "text": "seamlessly transitions into \"The Sunshine,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 739840.0,
      "end_time": 744376.0,
      "text": "or the haunting beauty of Luke Sital-Singh's \"Killing Me,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 744400.0,
      "end_time": 746960.0,
      "text": "whose chorus reads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 746120.0,
      "end_time": 749160.0,
      "text": "\"And it's killing me that you're not here with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 750800.0,
      "end_time": 753760.0,
      "text": "I'm living happily, but I'm feeling guilty.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 755800.0,
      "end_time": 760960.0,
      "text": "There is beauty in the simple moments that life has to offer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 760120.0,
      "end_time": 764496.0,
      "text": "a way of seeing that world that was so much a part of Amy's DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 764520.0,
      "end_time": 766536.0,
      "text": "like on my morning commute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 766560.0,
      "end_time": 769776.0,
      "text": "looking at the sun reflecting off of Lake Michigan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 769800.0,
      "end_time": 773295.0,
      "text": "or stopping and truly seeing how the light shines"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 773320.0,
      "end_time": 775536.0,
      "text": "at different times of the day"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 775560.0,
      "end_time": 778199.0,
      "text": "in the house we built together;"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 779400.0,
      "end_time": 783336.0,
      "text": "even after a Chicago storm, noticing the fresh buildup of snow"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 783360.0,
      "end_time": 785960.0,
      "text": "throughout the neighborhood;"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 785120.0,
      "end_time": 788456.0,
      "text": "or peeking into my daughter's room"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 788480.0,
      "end_time": 790720.0,
      "text": "as she's practicing the bass guitar."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 793280.0,
      "end_time": 797280.0,
      "text": "Listen, I want to make it clear that I'm a very fortunate person."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 798200.0,
      "end_time": 801840.0,
      "text": "I have the most amazing family that loves and supports me."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 802840.0,
      "end_time": 806240.0,
      "text": "I have the resources for personal growth during my time of grief."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 807680.0,
      "end_time": 809479.0,
      "text": "But whether it's a divorce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 810440.0,
      "end_time": 813136.0,
      "text": "losing a job you worked so hard at"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 813160.0,
      "end_time": 815256.0,
      "text": "or having a family member die suddenly"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 815280.0,
      "end_time": 817880.0,
      "text": "or of a slow-moving and painful death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 818880.0,
      "end_time": 820856.0,
      "text": "I would like to offer you"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 820880.0,
      "end_time": 822800.0,
      "text": "what I was given:"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 823320.0,
      "end_time": 825960.0,
      "text": "a blank of sheet of paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 827320.0,
      "end_time": 831800.0,
      "text": "What will you do with your intentional empty space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 831920.0,
      "end_time": 834920.0,
      "text": "with your fresh start?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 835880.0,
      "end_time": 837960.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 837120.0,
      "end_time": 842840.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}